						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Adventures in Zombiewood is a card and dice-based game that pits you and other unfortunate actors against a horde of Z-lebrities. In a world where the undead have overrun mankind, the only form of entertainment we have left is reenacting movies of times gone by.  Now it's your turn to shine as you remake your favorite zombie classics.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Adventures is Zombiewood is a cooperative game where players each command a different actor each turn.  They use the actor to take on the Z-lebrities that spawn during each Scene they are shooting.  They roll dice in an attempt to match the symbols required to defeat the Z-lebrity.  Anytime a player is unable to defeat the Z-lebrity, their actor is zombified and joins the growing horde to be faced in the game's final scene.  Combat must be fast (as you are trying to conserve film reel) so each combat phase is timed, and all players must be finished with their attack rolls before the timer signals the end of the scene.  Team strategy and quick thinking will give you a chance to survive to the end of your movie.  How many stars will your film earn... and will you survive to find out?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
